  "remarks": "LLC Testkomplekt supplies goods falling under Union restrictive measures to the Russian Federation. In particular, LLC Testkomplekt offers wide range of analogue-to-digital components, microcontrollers, diodes and sensors that cannot be exported to the Russian Federation. Furthermore, LLC Testkomplekt is a supplier of Radiopriborsnab, a subsidiary of Concern Radioelectronic Technologies (KRET), Russia’s major developer and manufacturer of military radio-electronic products.",
